Alembic async migration environment for Cognivest.

Generate a migration:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"
Apply migrations:
    alembic upgrade head

The database URL comes from application settings (settings.DATABASE_URL); the
value in alembic.ini is a placeholder. Versioned migration scripts live under
versions/. See src/database/migrations/env.py for the async setup.
